Document: PrismMesh  
Path: godot/classes/class_prismmesh.rst  
Summary: Properties and methods for controlling the shape and subdivision of a prism mesh in Godot.  

- left_to_right (float): Displacement of the upper edge along the X axis. 0.0 positions edge straight above the bottom-left edge. Default: 0.5. Methods: set_left_to_right(value: float), get_left_to_right().  
- size (Vector3): Size of the prism. Default: Vector3(1, 1, 1). Methods: set_size(value: Vector3), get_size().  
- subdivide_depth (int): Number of added edge loops along the Z axis. Default: 0. Methods: set_subdivide_depth(value: int), get_subdivide_depth().  
- subdivide_height (int): Number of added edge loops along the Y axis. Default: 0. Methods: set_subdivide_height(value: int), get_subdivide_height().  
- subdivide_width (int): Number of added edge loops along the X axis. Default: 0. Methods: set_subdivide_width(value: int), get_subdivide_width().